---
title: Smokey Sloppy Joes with Shredded Carrot Salad and Cilantro-Lime Vinaigrette
description: Get ready for a cafeteria throwback. We’re stepping up classic Sloppy Joes with pickled onion and deep, smoky spices. A crisp side salad with tangy dressing finishes off the dish with a bang.
